SUMMARY:Paired to Perfection: A Six Course Wine and Culinary Experience
DESCRIPTION:Paired to Perfection: A Six-Course Wine & Culinary Experience in Davis Saturday\, March 28 | 6:00–8:30 pm\nGet ready for an unforgettable evening where food and wine truly speak the same language.\nJoin us at Great Bear Vineyards for an elegant\, immersive dining experience featuring a six-course\, chef-crafted menu\, each dish thoughtfully paired with our estate-grown wines. This is more than dinner—it’s a journey through seasonal ingredients\, inspired techniques\, and wines designed to shine alongside every bite.\nEach course is carefully curated to highlight balance\, contrast\, and harmony between the plate and the glass—showcasing what happens when great food meets great wine \n Ticket Options:• Dinner Only: $65 + 20% gratuity = $78• Dinner + Paired Wines: $100 + 20% gratuity = $120\n Sample Menu (Inspired by Past Culinary Highlights):• Crisp Fish Tacos — paired with Albariño• Spicy Tuna Tartare — paired with Sauvignon Blanc• Slow-Braised Pork Belly — paired with Chardonnay Frizzante or Tempranillo 2021• Lamb Medallion — paired with Vintner’s Blend 2019• Steak & Mash — paired with Cabernet Sauvignon\, Grand Reserve 2020• Olive Oil Cake with Pistachio Icing — paired with our white port-style dessert wine\n Vegetarian guests welcome! A full vegetarian menu is available upon request.\nThis intimate evening is perfect for food lovers\, wine enthusiasts\, date nights\, or anyone who enjoys savoring life one course at a time. Come experience the essence of Great Bear Vineyards—where every sip and every bite tells a story of craftsmanship\, community\, and California wine country magic.\n Limited seating. Advance tickets required.
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/paired-to-perfection-a-six-course-wine-and-culinary-experience/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards  24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Great-Bear-Vineyards_23GBV-drone-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
